{"tid":1451493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:15:21.000Z","uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5592375abaef5481a1df7fa7363d267718c900f0","tid":1451493,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:13:21.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=447e9776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=9f457a3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"c9fd25700b4f1de727787b9a4aa978ca1adf120b","tid":1451493,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:14:51.000Z","msg":"【幫手推】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d7f714b09b8508219f17b867e69c62696e03117","tid":1451493,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUFT85U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt